      <section eId="sec_1570_J">
        <num>1570-J</num>
        <heading>Agreements of the village</heading>
        <subsection eId="sec_1570_J__subsec_a">
          <num>(a)</num>
          <content>
            <p>the bonds, together with interest thereon,\ninterest on any unpaid installments of interest and all costs and\nexpenses in connection with any action or proceeding by or on behalf of\nthe bondholders are fully met and discharged or</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_1570_J__subsec_b">
          <num>(b)</num>
          <content>
            <p>principal or\ninterest of any of the bonds shall be overdue and unpaid for a period of\nthree years or more, provided that nothing in this subdivision shall be\ndeemed to impair the right of the village to install and operate parking\nmeters on the public streets of the village.\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
      </section>
